default(2)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIt should not be possible to create a public right of way across the railway (dedicate a highway) impliedly. 
default(3)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStatutory rights of way should be trea
defaultted in the same way as easements if the owner agrees to sell the right of way (and therefore close the level crossing permanently) to the railway operator. 
