default1.36
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWe provided a total net present value of between £717 million and £1,464 million, with £1,402 being the best estimate
